data.description: Welcome homel Discover the charm of country living with this beautiful property in lovely Leisure Acres. This charming residence offers a perfect blend of space and comfort. The property is embraced by a fully fenced yard on half an acre that ensures plenty of privacy. Boasting three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this 1216 square-foot home is thoughtfully designed to maximize functionality without sacrificing style. The open-concept living spaces and well appointed kitchen make this home an ideal haven for both relaxation and entertaining! Come see what the Florida lifestyle on the nature coast is all about!
